item.title: Radiocarbon Data for Tree Ring Samples from Girdwood, Alaska
item.description: Abstract This dataset consists of sample details and radiocarbon age data of tree-ring samples collected near Girdwood, Alaska, and analyzed at the National Ocean Sciences Accelerator Mass Spectrometry Facility. Access Points https://alaska.usgs.gov/products/data.php?dataid=607
